  "id": "RAW_20280777",
  "title": "王华东：今年读了 30 本书，这是我的年度书单丨 2025 尾声",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=Mzk0MDMyNDUxOQ==&mid=2247496850&idx=1&sn=541a183dbd18ca33d93ba2d511b06721",
  "date": "2025-12-19 04:22:00",
  "author": "暗涌Waves",
  "siteName": "暗涌Waves",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"2 3 []\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100012929\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"960\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto !important;\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/BhIKFZ2E88hoSqwnbQibtJsZenH0WIM1S3h62LvnHUnIVoQ2YRkLfCnvicdDJEccccOufCHjicb9qweQfYe5B4hdA/0?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"578\" data-cropsely2=\"578\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=2fe282f5&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FBhIKFZ2E88hoSqwnbQibtJsZenH0WIM1S3h62LvnHUnIVoQ2YRkLfCnvicdDJEccccOufCHjicb9qweQfYe5B4hdA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-top: 24px;margin-bottom: 48px;text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 175, 0);\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">「</span></strong></span><span><strong><span leaf=\"\">勤奋、提炼、落地。</span></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 175, 0);\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">」</span></strong></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: right;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(178, 178, 178);font-size: 12px;\"><span leaf=\"\">文</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(0, 175, 0);\"><span leaf=\"\">｜</span></span><span style=\"font-size:12px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">经纬创投 王华东</span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: right;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100011910\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.12444444444444444\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"900\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto !important;\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"72\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=2d912896&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_gif%2FBhIKFZ2E88gzESQ19UqrtSgjbbIfXapAPVuIicnkFMjZ2m7IPq7oVSPKaK9lLSh3y154FrDKasnyaqiaKd9yF90A%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dgif\"></span></strong></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin: 24px 16px 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">处在时代的变革期，“转型”成为大到国家、小到个人都需要去思考和实践的事。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 24px 16px 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">投资人当然也一样。而在一级市场投资人这个群体中，围绕转型的对话，有一个名字总会在最开始就被提及——经纬创投管理合伙人王华东。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 24px 16px 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">在王华东身上，你很难看到那种不同赛道、不同产业、不同学科间的“断裂感”。从媒体人到投资人，从陌陌到理想汽车、沐曦和宇树，从文娱、消费、新能源生态，再到先进制造与AI相关的硬科技核心领域，他一次次完成了丝滑的迁移。这些看似跨度极大的选择，背后其实是一条清晰的技术与产业演进逻辑，而非简单的赛道轮换。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 24px 16px 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">我们曾经很好奇这种在投资行业罕见的“腾挪之术”，但每每与王华东聊起，得到的答案都有些轻描淡写。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 24px 16px 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">很多人都知道他是一个对自己极狠的人，像管理精密工程一样管理自己的生活与思想。这么多年有两件事雷打不动：第一，每天清晨五点半起床；第二，保持每年30本以上的高强度阅读。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 24px 16px 0px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 14px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;color: rgb(0, 175, 0);letter-spacing: 0.578px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">对他而言，阅读不是消遣，而是一种“认知补齐”与“规律迁移”的过程——</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 24px 16px 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">读通用汽车传奇CEO斯隆的传记，去理解100年前汽车产业链的演进逻辑，并以此作为判断新能源车的底层坐标；他还反复研读尤瓦尔·赫拉利，在人类演化的宏大尺度中寻找不同时代下的必然性。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 24px 16px 0px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 14px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;color: rgb(0, 175, 0);letter-spacing: 0.578px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">在王华东的视野里，技术和商业模式或许在变，但产业运行的底层逻辑、人性对效率的渴望、以及系统性泡沫的生成机制，在100年前与100年后并无二致。</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 24px 16px 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">如果说，上一代GP的成功核心是拓荒中国资本市场的胆量与独到的看人能力，而王华东所体现出新一代GP的特点之一是“科学投资观”下的精准布局。而这种精准来自对跨界知识的极限压榨。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 24px 16px 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">2018年钱颖一与马斯克在清华大学的对话曾给王华东留下极深的印象，他不止一次向我们分享其中的一个片段——</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 24px 16px 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">钱：分享一下你学习的秘密。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 24px 16px 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">马：读很多的书，和很多人交流。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 24px 16px 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">钱：光靠读书就可以成为一个火箭科学家？</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 24px 16px 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">马：是的。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 24px 16px 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">世间的运行逻辑或许就是如此残酷——</span></span><strong style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 14px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;color: rgb(0, 175, 0);letter-spacing: 0.578px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 14px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;color: rgb(0, 175, 0);letter-spacing: 0.578px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">很多成功背后可能的确没有过于高深的答案，无非是比你幸运的人还比你更加努力而已。</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">经纬创投张颖曾这样评价王华东，不仅善于学习，更难得的是极其勤奋，善于提炼，敢于落地。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 24px 16px 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">“他敢对抗自己的舒适区，也敢拿结果说话。”在张颖看来，这是王华东能够成长为GP的核心原因之一。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 24px 16px 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">这一次，王华东选择用一份年度书单来参与「暗涌Waves」的「2025尾声」。以下就是这份“非常王华东”的2025书单，排名不分先后。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 24px 16px 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">「2025尾声」仍在征集之中，欢迎商业世界和资本市场的思考者们通过后台或</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">chenzhiyan@36kr.com</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">与我们联系。相信，时代变幻，唯真正的思考不灭。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: right;margin: 40px 16px 8px;line-height: 1.6em;\" data-pm-slice=\"4 4 []\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">Part</span></strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 24px;color: rgb(0, 175, 0);\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">01</span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: right;margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 24px;color: rgb(0, 175, 0);\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">认知商业</span></strong></span></p>\n  <h3 data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin: 32px 16px 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:14px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 20px;\">《泡沫逃生》</span></span></h3>\n  <p style=\"margin: 24px 16px 0px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.6em;letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">作者：阿拉斯戴尔·奈恩</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 24px 16px 0px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.6em;letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">副标题：技术进步与科技投资简史</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 24px 16px 0px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.6em;letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">原作名：Engines That Move Markets: Technology Investing from Railroads to the Internet and Beyond</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 24px 16px 0px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.6em;letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">简介：所有的疯狂都有迹可循，作者通过复盘从运河到互联网的五次浪潮，揭示了技术如何从改变世界沦为投机者的狂欢。这是一部横跨200年的“避坑指南”，它告诉你当下的AI热潮在历史的铁路、电力泡沫中能找到哪些惊人相似的韵脚。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 24px 16px 0px;line-height: 1.6em;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100012872\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.4111111111111112\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width: 420px;height: auto !important;\" data-width=\"1080\" data-height=\"1524\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=9845b4a1&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FBhIKFZ2E88jlWRibxziciavwjlGVsibxdic0k7dOzEC3SsKJJMf1Q0FgvVF4vUhhVnDTsdIHMOaOW35d83meYIM3ibyA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></span></p>\n  <h3 style=\"margin: 32px 16px 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:14px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 20px;\">《高增长科技股投资法》</span></span></h3>\n  <p style=\"margin: 24px 16px 0px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.6em;letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">作者：马克·马哈尼</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 24px 16px 0px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.6em;letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">原作名：Nothing But Net</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 24px 16px 0px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.6em;letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">简介：摒弃对“概念”的盲从，本书提供了一套评估高增长公司的硬性框架，强调长期趋势与商业逻辑才是投资的压舱石。硅谷顶级分析师的“扫雷手册”，教你如何在喧嚣的趋势中，用冷静的基本面锚点抓住下一个时代的真正赢家。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-top: 24px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_jpg/BhIKFZ2E88jlWRibxziciavwjlGVsibxdic0kQciaJfrp2kJ8Uib1cX6gnVUxicrHEtJPUxguYibjic2Cs4b0ZeoBIM4CdWw/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropx1=\"66.10989010989012\" data-cropx2=\"576.7032967032967\" data-cropy2=\"640\" data-height=\"640\" data-imgfileid=\"100012871\" data-ratio=\"1.2549019607843137\" style=\"width: 412px;height: auto !important;\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"510\" data-width=\"640\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=d94ae60f&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FBhIKFZ2E88hoSqwnbQibtJsZenH0WIM1SRCvLRUpVzEUeFIx4UGWUk4gO2rDJ9tEs9KlU4pntibYCEictRRiaqwu5g%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 24px 16px 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 14px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;color: rgb(0, 175, 0);letter-spacing: 0.578px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">——当下各方都在热议AI Bubble，不妨了解下历史上出现过的产业和科技泡沫到底是怎么回事，同时，也值得去了解下怎么选择投资科技股。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: right;margin: 40px 16px 8px;line-height: 1.6em;\" data-pm-slice=\"4 4 []\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">Part</span></strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 24px;color: rgb(0, 175, 0);\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">02</span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: right;margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 24px;color: rgb(0, 175, 0);\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">审</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"text-align: right;line-height: 1.6em;font-size: 24px;color: rgb(0, 175, 0);font-weight: bold;\">视生</span><span leaf=\"\">活</span></strong></span></p>\n  <h3 data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin: 32px 16px 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:14px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 20px;\">《我们为什么要睡觉》</span></span></h3>\n  <p style=\"margin: 24px 16px 0px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.6em;letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">作者：马修·沃克</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 24px 16px 0px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.6em;letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">副标题：关于睡眠和梦的科学新发现</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 24px 16px 0px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.6em;letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(8