m;letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">副标题：重新定义成功、睡眠与幸福</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 24px 16px 0px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.6em;letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">原作名：The Sleep Revolution: Transforming Your Life, One Night at a Time</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 24px 16px 0px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.6em;letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">简介：作者从个人经历与科学研究出发，批判“以透支睡眠换取成功”的文化，倡导将高质量睡眠作为提升效率、健康与长期幸福的核心基础。书中丰富的科学案例能帮助人们轻松理解睡眠与幸福感的关系。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 24px 16px 0px;line-height: 1.6em;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100012877\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.4351851851851851\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width: 424px;height: auto !important;\" data-width=\"1080\" data-height=\"1550\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=926853a3&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FBhIKFZ2E88jlWRibxziciavwjlGVsibxdic0kOWiaQLVl0qibAh89u50Pz3reEar92JrKibOSxy1NteTJp37n2icQYGnGNA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 24px 16px 0px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 14px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;color: rgb(0, 175, 0);letter-spacing: 0.578px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">——了解睡眠对每个人都非常重要。这两本书里有很多故事，会帮你很容易理解睡眠的神奇之处。</span></span></strong></p>\n  <h3 style=\"margin: 32px 16px 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:14px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 20px;\">《跑步圣经》</span></span></h3>\n  <p style=\"margin: 24px 16px 0px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.6em;letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">作者：乔治·希恩</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 24px 16px 0px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.6em;letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">原作名：Running and Being:The Total Experience</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 24px 16px 0px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.6em;letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">简介：跑步，究竟是一场苦行僧之旅，还是跑者内心的一场博弈？一个跑者的世界究竟是什么样子？这是一本融合实践和哲学的跑步著作。通过这本书，也许能够找到“你到底是谁”和“你该如何适应你自己”的答案。</span></span></p>\n  <div style=\"margin: 24px 16px 0px;line-height: 1.6em;text-align: center;\">\n   <div>\n    <p style=\"display: inline-block;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img style=\"height: auto !important;\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.528358208955224\" data-type=\"jpg\" data-w=\"1340\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=670cf0c7&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FBhIKFZ2E88hoSqwnbQibtJsZenH0WIM1SR3goc4PrSj4U37KVGv7XGWVz1HGp5R5pxmopuFHue0BDBpAX6CYibFw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <h3 style=\"margin: 32px 16px 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:14px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 20px;\">《天生就会跑》</span></span></h3>\n  <p style=\"margin: 24px 16px 0px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.6em;letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">作者：克里斯托弗·麦克杜格尔</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 24px 16px 0px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.6em;letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">原作名：Born to Run: A Hidden Tribe, Superathletes, and the Greatest Race the World Has Never Seen</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 24px 16px 0px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.6em;letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">简介：通过追寻塔拉乌马拉族的跑步文化，融合人类进化、生理学与个人体验，探讨人类为何“天生适合跑步”以及跑步的本源意义。这是一场关于人类进化史的浪漫探寻，它会告诉你，奔跑不仅是运动，更是刻在智人DNA里最原始的生存与快乐本能。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 24px 16px 0px;line-height: 1.6em;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100012876\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.512\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1000\" style=\"color: rgb(85, 85, 85);font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;width: 420px;height: auto !important;\" data-width=\"1000\" data-height=\"1512\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=855fb58f&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FBhIKFZ2E88jlWRibxziciavwjlGVsibxdic0kKut1Z6P9Q9Ys6bDZAhic5CNAF0cYsKBpNyE1stvlh2mwEGPm9sPdVjA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 24px 16px 0px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><strong style=\"letter-spacing: 0.034em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;color: rgb(0, 175, 0);letter-spacing: 0.578px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">——决定跑步后我就读了这两本书。很多人觉得跑步简单，有些人觉得跑步无聊，当你对跑步了解更多之后，你会</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;color: rgb(0, 175, 0);letter-spacing: 0.578px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">发现跑好步不容易，跑步其实很有乐趣。</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 24px 16px 0px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;color: rgb(0, 175, 0);letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-size: 15px;\">PS：我今年1月首马（厦门马拉松）4:10:14，到11月的上海马拉松3:22:49，马拉松成绩提高了47分钟25秒。</span></strong></p>\n  <h2 style=\"text-align: right;margin: 40px 16px 0px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"text-align: right;line-height: 1.6em;font-size: 24px;color: rgb(0, 175, 0);font-weight: bold;\">洞察世界</span></h2>\n  <h3 style=\"margin: 32px 16px 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:14px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 20px;\">《智人之上》</span></span></h3>\n  <p style=\"margin: 24px 16px 0px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.6em;letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">作者：尤瓦尔·赫拉利</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 24px 16px 0px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.6em;letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">副标题：从智人到人工智能的信息网络简史</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 24px 16px 0px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.6em;letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">原作名：Nexus: A Brief History of Information Networks from the Stone Age to AI</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 24px 16px 0px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.6em;letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">简介：当AI接管了信息的编织权，赫拉利再次发出预警：这不只是一场技术革命，更是一次对人类数千年社会结构根基的暴力重塑。他以“信息网络”为主线，梳理了从远古叙事到现代算法的演化，揭示了信息如何成为塑造未来文明的核心力量。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 24px 16px 0px;line-height: 1.6em;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100012875\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.513622603430878\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"991\" style=\"width: 422px;height: auto !important;\" data-width=\"991\" data-height=\"1500\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=a547fc76&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FBhIKFZ2E88jlWRibxziciavwjlGVsibxdic0kvYbCXxnbtjuxzn598UYvNq7YRicWRxmeQEoU1NOMZkAk2srsHu6MynA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></span></p>\n  <h3 style=\"margin: 32px 16px 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:14px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 20px;\">赫拉利简史三部曲</span></span></h3>\n  <h3 style=\"margin: 8px 16px 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:14px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 20px;\">《人类简史》、《未来简史》、《今日简史》</span></span></h3>\n  <p style=\"margin: 24px 16px 0px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.6em;letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">简介：“上帝视角”三部曲，用虚构秩序、算法与数据主义的逻辑，复盘了人类如何从荒原走上神坛。这套书重新定义了权力、政治与个人选择。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 24px 16px 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100012886\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5027777777777778\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"text-align: center;letter-spacing: 0.034em;width: 541px;height: auto !important;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=1fc0b1bd&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FBhIKFZ2E88jlWRibxziciavwjlGVsibxdic0kCibP9egAmHiaCsumfokH7z2lr7HbMIic4cMIDIhDba4TlblHUfedkcc3w%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 24px 16px 0px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 14px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;color: rgb(0, 175, 0);letter-spacing: 0.578px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">——接着智人之上把赫拉利的简史三部曲又重新读了一遍。我们了解了很多人类的过去，随着科技尤其是</span></span></strong><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 14px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;color: rgb(0, 175, 0);letter-spacing: 0.578px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">AI</span></span></strong><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 14px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;color: rgb(0, 175, 0);letter-spacing: 0.578px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">的发展，我们需要花更多时间思考人类的未来。</span></span></strong></p>\n  <h2 style=\"text-align: right;margin: 40px 16px 0px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"text-align: right;line-height: 1.6em;font-size: 24px;color: rgb(0, 175, 0);font-weight: bold;\">理解人</span></h2>\n  <h3 style=\"margin: 32px 16px 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:14px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 20px;\">《张忠谋自传（上下册）》</span></span></h3>\n  <p style=\"margin: 24px 16px 0px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.6em;letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">作者：张忠谋</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 24px 16px 0px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.6em;letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">简介：半导体教父近一个世纪的孤绝长征，书里藏着台积电如何用“诚信”与“专业分工”统治全球算力底座的终极秘密。它不只是一位企业家的编年史，更是一部半导体产业的演进史，展现了长期主义如何重构全球商业格局。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 24px 16px 0px;line-height: 1.6em;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100012885\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5916666666666667\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width: 472px;height: auto !important;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=f58491fd&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FBhIKFZ2E88jlWRibxziciavwjlGVsibxdic0kf9GgaYDJ48NweDX6Z3GAIbjcuRibDzx1R26QoWV6WYHlmd3zib9icQ1sQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 24px 16px 0px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 14px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;color: rgb(0, 175, 0);letter-spacing: 0.578px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">——希望我也能成为学习不止的人。我想台积电的企业文化就是张忠谋做人的体现。</span></span></strong></p>\n  <h3 style=\"margin: 32px 16px 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:14px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 20px;\">《征服市场的人》</span></span></h3>\n  <p style=\"margin: 24px 16px 0px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.6em;letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">作者：格里高利·祖克曼</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 24px 16px 0px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.6em;letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">副标题：文艺复兴基金的传奇</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 24px 16px 0px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.6em;letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">原作名：The Man Who Solved the Market</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 24px 16px 0px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.6em;letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">简介：揭秘“量化投资之神”西蒙斯如何用一群数学天才打败了华尔街，证明了在充满随机性的市场中，客观模型比人类直觉更接近真相。其中讲述了文艺复兴基金是如何颠覆传统投资逻辑，并揭开了数据驱动、模型导向这类“先进生产力”的思想源头。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 24px 16px 0px;line-height: 1.6em;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100012884\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.3518518518518519\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width: 420px;height: auto !important;\" data-width=\"1080\" data-height=\"1460\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=ea637b94&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FBhIKFZ2E88jlWRibxziciavwjlGVsibxdic0kIiaAJ6pGeq7iaOzx1eRaPFg7iaKpS9YrJgdYBpiaRCRVib2Gb82HWQaPrwA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 24px 16px 0px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 14px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;color: rgb(0, 175, 0);letter-spacing: 0.578px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">——很多人读《征服市场的人》是在DeepSeek爆火后，因为梁文锋给这本书作序。我也是因为这原因读的。西蒙斯的成功之处，最重要的一点就是招募最牛X的人，并给他们一个好环境。</span></span></strong></p>\n  <h3 style=\"margin: 32px 16px 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:14px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 20px;\">《岩田先生》</span></span></h3>\n  <p style=\"margin: 24px 16px 0px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.6em;letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">作者：岩田聪 口述，糸井重里 编</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 24px 16px 0px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.6em;letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">原作名：岩田さん：岩田聡語る</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 24px 16px 0px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.6em;letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">简介：记录了任天堂前社长岩田聪如何平衡商业逻辑与玩家同理心，将平凡的工作转化为感动世界的产品。这本书是一位技术天才转型社长的温暖自白，诠释了如何用“开发者”的匠心去解决最复杂的“管理”难题。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 24px 16px 0px;line-height: 1.6em;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100012883\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.4407407407407407\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width: 423px;height: auto !important;\" data-width=\"1080\" data-height=\"1556\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=7ec93dd4&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FBhIKFZ2E88jlWRibxziciavwjlGVsibxdic0kXOo5NFNwozuhjiapOAWp0KlgwJV68H7mOrricMskbiayvr9RyCrFHM7Pg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></span></p>\n  <div>\n   <p style=\"margin: 24px 16px 0px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 14px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;color: rgb(0, 175, 0);letter-spacing: 0.578px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">——所有对游戏感兴趣的人都应该读一下这本书。岩田先生的一个自我总结充分说明了他的伟大之处。</span></span></strong></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 24px 16px 0px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;color: rgb(0, 175, 0);letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-size: 15px;\">在我的名片上，我是一名社长；在我的头脑中，我是一名游戏开发者；但在我心里，我是一个玩家。</span></strong></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"margin: 32px 16px 0px;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-size: 12px;color: rgb(178, 178, 178);\"><span leaf=\"\">排版｜姚楠</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px 16px;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-size: 12px;color: 